<h1>如何安装Atom插件</h1>

<p>Atom是一款功能十分强大的编辑器，atom里有许多非常实用的插件，也有很多有趣的插件，例如minimap，activate-power-mode,下面介绍如何在atom下安装插件。</p>

<p><a href="https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html">源网页</a></p>

<h2>方法1</h2>

<ol>
	<li>
	<p>点击<strong>file</strong>，然后点击<strong>settings</strong></p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=1" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=cf628c82d6c451daf6f60ceb86ff52a5/b64543a98226cffccaa0ab6eb2014a90f703ea60.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>单击<strong>install</strong></p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=2" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=7c7e77a29958d109c4e3a9b2e159ccd0/c2cec3fdfc03924577a2f5d38c94a4c27c1e25d2.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>输入你想要下载的插件名称，即可下载安装</p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=3" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=7fbb76a29958d109c4e3a9b2e15accd0/c2cec3fdfc0392457467f4d38c94a4c27c1e251f.jpg" /></a></p>

	<p>END</p>
	</li>
</ol>

<h2>方法2</h2>

<ol>
	<li>
	<p>键盘组合键<strong>WIN+R</strong>，输入cmd并回车</p>

	<p>打开命令行窗口</p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=4" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=17f1883ff61f4134e037057e151d95c1/80cb39dbb6fd526661f929c8a018972bd507361f.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>输入apm install空格加你想要下载的包名称，即可下载</p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=5" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=02012d3b9a2397ddd67998046983b216/ae51f3deb48f8c54f3d7d1f331292df5e1fe7fe1.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>重启ATOM即可安装成功</p>

	<p>END</p>
	</li>
</ol>

<h2>方法3</h2>

<ol>
	<li>
	<p>在Github上下载相应的插件</p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=6" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=031fc431ec1190ef01fb92dffe1a9df7/32fa828ba61ea8d37b3560d89c0a304e241f58d2.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>解压并复制到C盘的如下目录</p>

	<p><strong>c-用户-电脑名-.atom-pakages</strong></p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=7" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=4ef061d89c0a304e5222a0fae1caa7c3/b7fd5266d016092418f7b7c7df0735fae7cd341f.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>如同方法二，打开命令行窗口输入 apm install 重启Atom即可</p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=8" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=d408163d242eb938ec6d7af2e56085fe/d058ccbf6c81800a99379cd2ba3533fa838b471f.jpg" /></a></p>

	<p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/86112f138d2a1d273797879d.html?picindex=9" target="_self"><img alt="如何安装Atom插件" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/exp/w=500/sign=99d893fd9813b07ebdbd50083cd69113/77c6a7efce1b9d169fd08ebdf8deb48f8d5464d2.jpg" /></a></p>
	</li>
</ol>
